 -
 - Function:                    Test:                   Notes:
 - securePkg_init               correct keyExpand       implicit
 - securePkg_zero               nada
 - securePkg_enc_in_place       correctness             interop
 - securePkg_dec                correctness             interop
 - securePkg_enc                correctness             interop
 -}
